CompetenceLevelKD_110.notes: The observer has basic skills to assess avalanche danger. The observer is not educated in how regObs and Varsom communicates avalanche danger.

CompetenceLevelKD_110_desc.translation: Opazovalec ima osnovna znanja za oceno nevarnosti snežnih plazov, nima pa izobrazbe glede načina komunikacije nevarnosti snežnih plazov v okviru regObs in Varsom.

CompetenceLevelKD_130_desc.translation: Opazovalec je izobražen in ima napredna znanja za oceno nevarnosti snežnih plazov. Deležen je bil naprednega izobraževanja glede načina komunikacije nevarnosti snežnih plazov v okviru regObs in Varsom.

IceCoverBeforeKD_1.notes: No ice at site before today. There may have been ice along the shore. "Site" is generally a virtual point out on the lake away from the shore.

IceCoverBeforeKD_10.notes: Continuous observations. We can assume that the ice cover from previous observation is valid until yeaterday. Today is a new value (or the same ice cover)

IceCoverBeforeKD_10_desc.translation: Neprekinjena opažanja. Lahko sklepamo, da je obseg ledene površine s prejšnjega opažanja veljaven do včerajšnjega dne. Danes je lahko vrednost drugačna (ali pa enaka).

IceCoverBeforeKD_1_desc.translation: Pred današnjim dnem na območju opažanja ni bilo ledu. Led je morda bil ob obali. "Območje opažanja" je v splošnem navidezna točka na jezeru, ki ni ob obali.
IceCoverBeforeKD_1_desc.notes: No ice, now first ice at site

IceCoverBeforeKD_2.translation: Brez ledu, prvič led na obali
IceCoverBeforeKD_2.notes: No ice along the shore before today.

IceCoverBeforeKD_2_desc.translation: Pred današnjim dnem ob obali ni bilo ledu.
IceCoverBeforeKD_2_desc.notes: No ice, now first ice at shore

IceCoverBeforeKD_3.translation: Brez ledu do sedaj, tudi danes
IceCoverBeforeKD_3.notes: No ice this winter season, not even today.

IceCoverBeforeKD_3_desc.translation: Brez ledu v tekoči zimski sezoni, vključno z današnjim dnem.
IceCoverBeforeKD_3_desc.notes: No ice so far, including today

IceCoverBeforeKD_99.notes: Break in measurements. The ice cover from previous observation is probably not valid until yeaterday.

IceCoverBeforeKD_99_desc.translation: Napaka pri meritvah. Opažen obseg ledene površine s prejšnjega opažanja verjetno ne predstavlja dejanskega stanja do včeraj.
